# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# slide-svg — environment variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# slide-svg currently has no required env vars. AI image generation
# uses the bundled `/codex-image` skill (Codex CLI OAuth → gpt-image-2,
# no API key needed). See README.md "4단계" for the one-time setup
# (`npm install -g @openai/codex && codex login`).
#
# Copy this file to `.env` only if you add project-local secrets later;
# `.env` is git-ignored.
